{"tid":1591913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急！推比大昌行租車部巴打見到","createTime":"2019-09-24T11:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T09:51:11.000Z","uid":282650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"860f490cefed36668e41d2eb5495643a02421e09","tid":1591913,"uid":282650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"有人fc VR3206同NN4044係大昌行登記<br />\n（唔係姓張個個呀，個個只係今日負責處理單case比人1999炒埋一碟spin錯方向架咋）<br />\n即係9成9係大昌行租車，popo有時會用合約式同車行租車，車行交架車比佢用，未必日日同一架，但照計大昌行實有紀錄派過車比咩人。<br />\n如果證實到呢兩架車係尋日派左比popo，就可以9成肯定尋日msg內容係真。因為正常無人會知租車租左比popo再屈佢。但大昌行肯定唔會講，只有靠內部自己友講出黎，而如果租車資料有人做手腳或者收埋哂都可以知係咩人租啦。<br />\n而家資料唔多，呢個線索好緊要，要快唔好比人快一步！"},{"pid":"a1f64c8b1f8f868a0cb140bd30b281cccfdb139c","tid":1591913,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"8c74f7335e8bd6eea5a984536259b9c12d4a46e2","tid":1591913,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de9f0adf2ff4f06c20906412648d44ce7c5bd016","tid":1591913,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ecda5965331e82f5101f8e2abf41c86403e20f9","tid":1591913,"uid":37922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:49:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c127a08eff23ec72ba95091ff6d72a56877414e0","tid":1591913,"uid":293791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:51:11.000Z","msg":"之前聽過 popo成日都係大昌行租車"}]}